Installation
------------

CBC.PDESys and subpackages depends on the latest version of FEniCS. To 
obtain FEniCS on Ubuntu simply do

  sudo apt-get install fenics

Otherwise see www.fenicsproject.org/installation/installation.html

CBC.PDESys also make use of python packages numpy, scipy and matplotlib.
These packages can be installed on Ubuntu through

  sudo apt-get install python-numpy python-scipy python-matplotlib

To install CBC.PDESys use regular distutils

  python setup.py install
